post_text:
Couldn't have asked for a smoother Chromebook distribution day! In just three hours, we distributed over 6,000 devices to #PowayUnified students and families who requested access to them. Thank you to #TeamPUSD staff volunteers for making this step toward distance learning a smooth one. We are humbled.

*If you requested a device AND filled out the Device Distribution Form prior to the April 1 deadline, but were unable to pick up today: Make-up check out time scheduled at ALL school sites for Friday, April 3rd between 3 pm and 4:30 pm.*

